{"tid":985134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微軟擬撥款5億美元西雅圖建平價房助低下層","createTime":"2019-01-17T10:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T11:06:28.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3cc69f4fca3ec52ae092409d716a59f5826cea","tid":985134,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"據美國傳媒報道，微軟擬撥款5億元(美元‧下同)(約39億港元)幫助解決西雅圖低收入人士無家可歸問題。<br />\n<br />\n微軟日前宣布，計劃利用該筆資金在西雅圖普吉特灣地區開發平價、可負擔的住房，為中低收入工人提供住房選擇。<br />\n<br />\n該筆5億美元的資金將用於開發數萬套公寓，其中2.25億元以低於市場的利率貸款予開發商、2.5億元按市場利率貸款，用於經濟房建造；剩下的2500萬元捐贈予低收入和無家可歸的人群。<br />\n<br />\n微軟總裁史密斯(Brad Smith)在報告中表示，僅靠微軟的資金不足以解決這些住房問題，他並敦促東區城市各市長盡快解決阻礙經濟適用房開發的政策壁壘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2041015/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E6%93%AC39%E5%84%84%E8%A5%BF%E9%9B%85%E5%9C%96%E5%BB%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%83%B9%E6%88%BF%E5%8A%A9%E4%BD%8E%E4%B8%8B%E5%B1%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2041015%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BB%259F%25E6%2593%25AC39%25E5%2584%2584%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E9%259B%2585%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%258A%25A9%25E4%25BD%258E%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%25B1%25A4&d=3m4rN%2F1AIvPT8ELKuhEPHtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=27279ee2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2041015/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E6%93%AC39%E5%84%84%E8%A5%BF%E9%9B%85%E5%9C%96%E5%BB%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%83%B9%E6%88%BF%E5%8A%A9%E4%BD%8E%E4%B8%8B%E5%B1%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20160814/720pix/1471171763_8924.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160814%2F720pix%2F1471171763_8924.jpg&h=39e5c12e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad8bd7fcf64a1b4b9f950dd9c26f73d1dd57161c","tid":985134,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:54:20.000Z","msg":"微軟捐錢拓市"}